---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	regionSlug="in"
	signupEnabled={true}
	served={true}
	served={false}
	signupEnabled={false}
	title="About Lucoze — Healthcare Technology Company — India"
	description="Learn about Lucoze and our mission to simplify healthcare management worldwide."
	activeLink="about"
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Lucoze</h1>
			<p>Making world-class healthcare management accessible to every facility.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="content-page">
		<div class="container" style="max-width: 800px">
			<h2>Our Story</h2>
			<p>
				Lucoze was founded by healthcare professionals and technologists who witnessed first-hand
				the painful gap between expensive, bloated enterprise systems and the inadequate
				spreadsheets that most clinics were forced to rely on. Doctors were spending more time
				wrestling with software than caring for patients. Lab technicians were printing results and
				manually filing them. Pharmacists were tracking inventory on paper.
			</p>
			<p>
				We set out to change that. Our mission is to democratize healthcare management technology —
				to give every clinic, hospital, diagnostic centre, and pharmacy access to the same powerful
				tools that were once reserved for large hospital chains with million-dollar IT budgets.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				We believe that every healthcare facility, regardless of size or location, deserves software
				that truly understands their workflows. From solo practitioners running a single
				consultation room to sprawling hospital networks with hundreds of departments, Lucoze adapts
				to the way healthcare is actually delivered — across every country, every specialty, and
				every scale. Our goal is simple: let healthcare professionals focus on patients, not
				paperwork.
			</p>

			<div class="about-values">
				<div class="about-value">
					<div class="about-value__icon">&#x1F6E1;&#xFE0F;</div>
					<h3>Healthcare First</h3>
					<p>
						Every feature is designed with healthcare workflows in mind. We build for doctors,
						nurses, lab technicians, and pharmacists.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="about-value">
					<div class="about-value__icon">&#x1F512;</div>
					<h3>Privacy by Design</h3>
					<p>
						Patient data security is non-negotiable. End-to-end encryption, regional data residency,
						and strict access controls are built into every layer.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="about-value">
					<div class="about-value__icon">&#x1F310;</div>
					<h3>Global, Local</h3>
					<p>
						One platform that works worldwide. Automatic compliance configuration, local tax
						templates, and multi-currency billing for every market.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2>The Company</h2>
			<p>
				Lucoze is built by <strong>Svasamm Research Pvt. Ltd.</strong>, headquartered in India. We
				are a technology company dedicated to building solutions that solve real problems in
				healthcare delivery, operations, and administration. Our team combines deep healthcare
				domain expertise with modern software engineering to create products that healthcare
				professionals actually enjoy using.
			</p>
			<p>
				Want to get in touch? Reach us at <a href="mailto:info@lucoze.com">info@lucoze.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
